<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><alert xmlns="urn:oasis:names:tc:emergency:cap:1.2"><identifier>2.49.0.0.554.0.tswarning.ch.20251227011411299.0</identifier><sender>https://www.metservice.com</sender><sent>2025-12-27T14:14:11+13:00</sent><status>Actual</status><msgType>Alert</msgType><scope>Public</scope><info><category>Met</category><event>Thunderstorm</event><responseType>Prepare</responseType><urgency>Immediate</urgency><severity>Severe</severity><certainty>Observed</certainty><onset>2025-12-27T14:00:00+13:00</onset><expires>2025-12-27T15:00:00+13:00</expires><senderName>Meteorological Service of New Zealand Limited</senderName><headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning</headline><description>At 02:00 pm, MetService weather radar detected severe thunderstorms near CAVE, PLEASANT POINT and ALBURY.

These severe thunderstorms are moving towards the north, and are expected to lie near CAVE, PLEASANT POINT, ALBURY and BEAUTIFUL VALLEY at 02:30 pm and near FAIRLIE, CAVE, ALBURY and BEAUTIFUL VALLEY at 03:00 pm.

These thunderstorms are expected to be accompanied by very heavy rain and large hail.

Impact:

Very heavy rain can cause surface and/or flash flooding about streams, gullies and urban areas, and make driving conditions extremely hazardous.

Large hail can cause significant damage to crops, orchards, vines, glasshouses and vehicles, and make driving conditions hazardous.</description><instruction>The National Emergency Management Agency advises that as storms approach you should:
    - Take shelter, preferably indoors away from windows;
    - Avoid sheltering under trees, if outside;
    - Get back to land, if outdoors on the water;
    - Move cars under cover or away from trees;
    - Secure any loose objects around your property;
    - Check that drains and gutters are clear;
    - Be ready to slow down or stop, if driving.
During and after the storm, you should also:
    - Beware of fallen trees and power lines;
    - Avoid streams and drains as you may be swept away in flash flooding.</instruction><web>https://www.metservice.com/warnings/home</web><parameter><valueName>ColourCode</valueName><value>Red</value></parameter><parameter><valueName>ColourCodeHex</valueName><value>#FF181E</value></parameter><area><areaDesc>Timaru,Mackenzie,Waimate</areaDesc><polygon>-44.068,170.857 -44.063,170.838 -44.061,170.818 -44.065,170.805 -44.070,170.794 -44.082,170.782 -44.096,170.775 -44.137,170.768 -44.166,170.769 -44.207,170.781 -44.245,170.790 -44.269,170.801 -44.292,170.819 -44.312,170.846 -44.343,170.893 -44.364,170.928 -44.386,170.974 -44.398,170.998 -44.406,171.046 -44.406,171.065 -44.403,171.085 -44.396,171.101 -44.387,171.115 -44.356,171.148 -44.332,171.158 -44.309,171.160 -44.277,171.160 -44.255,171.158 -44.228,171.151 -44.206,171.137 -44.179,171.110 -44.161,171.086 -44.144,171.048 -44.132,171.022 -44.111,170.982 -44.092,170.927 -44.076,170.886 -44.068,170.857</polygon></area></info><Signature xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#"><SignedInfo><CanonicalizationMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/TR/2001/REC-xml-c14n-20010315#WithComments"/><SignatureMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2001/04/xmldsig-more#rsa-sha256"/><Reference URI=""><Transforms><Transform Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#enveloped-signature"/></Transforms><DigestMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2001/04/xmlenc#sha256"/><DigestValue>AbaEY10HSPZOEku8K+t6/+HoFFJ2uK1AXma95e5zPJ8=</DigestValue></Reference></SignedInfo><SignatureValue>UWGEXrvLL2QrGRyu1Ooqsv+yoK5wL/3CB3pg6WeWhYjQyXtt/dqiPuvnJUF/l/S2JtPWns0LMN4U&#13;
